<P>
   &UR; ATTENTION ALL ``STAR WARS'' FANATICS: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   The first 10 editors to fax the correct answer to the following
``Star Wars'' trivia question to 212-499-3382 will receive a New
York Times mug and baseball cap!
</P>
<P>
   -----------------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   Besides assuming the role of Obi-Wan Kenobi, originally played
by Alec Guinness, what other connection does Ewan McGregor have to
the first ``Stars Wars'' trilogy?
</P>
<P>
   -----------------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   Run to your fax machine!
</P>
<P>
   Now that we've gotten your attention ...
</P>
<P>
   Doing anything fun with your entertainment and lifestyle pages
to cover the premiere of the latest ``Star Wars'' film?
</P>
<P>
