<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET- </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
April 22 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BBN-DODGERS-BRAVES (Los Angeles) _ The Los Angeles Dodgers face the
Atlanta Braves at 7:35 p.m. PDT. 
