<P>
   COLO-SCHOOL-SUSPECTS (Littleton, Colo.) _ The two Columbine High
School juniors worked last Friday making pizzas. On Monday, they
went bowling. And on Tuesday, it seems, they committed mass murder.
Nobody had taken Eric Harris and Dylan Klebold seriously. By Dirk
Johnson.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.)
</P>
